KW  - Amenities
KW  - Lifetime wage profile
AB  - Job amenities are explicitly included in a model of job choice over the life cycle. The amenities are characterized by an indivisibility—a worker must be present at a job to enjoy its amenities. This characterization has implications on initial job choice, a worker's wage profile and whether they move to a higher or lower paying job.
